---
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout
  title="WhatsApp for CPA Firms - Automated Reminders & Document Collection | HeshbonAI"
  description="Automate client reminders and document collection via WhatsApp. 82% response rate vs 23% for email. Built for accounting firms worldwide."
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: "Home", url: "https://heshbonai.co/" },
    { name: "WhatsApp for Accountants", url: "https://heshbonai.co/whatsapp-accounting/" }
  ]}
>
  <Navbar />
  <main>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="bg-navy pt-32 pb-16">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
        <span class="section-label">WhatsApp for CPA Firms</span>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mt-4 leading-tight">
          WhatsApp for CPA firms — automated reminders that actually work
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-muted mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Your clients don't respond to emails. They do respond on WhatsApp.
          <strong class="text-offwhite">82% response rate on WhatsApp</strong> vs 23% for email.
          Automated client reminders, document collection, and tracking — all through the channel your clients already use every day.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mt-10">
          <a href="https://cal.com/heshbonai/intro" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">
            Schedule your intro call
          </a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4">
            See Pricing
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem Section -->
    <section class="bg-navy-light py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <span class="section-label">The Problem</span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mt-4">
            Why emails and portals don't work
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">23% email response rate</h3>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              Send a client an email asking for documents? Most likely it won't get opened. It gets buried among 200 other messages, and you have to follow up again and again.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 1.5H8.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 3.75v16.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25h7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 20.25V3.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H13.5m-3 0V3h3V1.5m-3 0h3m-3 18.75h3" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">No client will download a portal</h3>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              You bought a system with a "client portal"? Nice. Now try convincing a 55-year-old business owner to download an app, create a password, and upload files. It just doesn't happen.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.625 12a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H8.25m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H12m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0h-.375M21 12c0 4.556-4.03 8.25-9 8.25a9.764 9.764 0 01-2.555-.337A5.972 5.972 0 015.41 20.97a5.969 5.969 0 01-.474-.065 4.48 4.48 0 00.978-2.025c.09-.457-.133-.901-.467-1.226C3.93 16.178 3 14.189 3 12c0-4.556 4.03-8.25 9-8.25s9 3.694 9 8.25z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">WhatsApp — where your clients are</h3>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              Over 2 billion people use WhatsApp daily worldwide. It's the most natural channel for business communication. Messages are read within 3 minutes on average.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section class="bg-navy py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-14">
          <span class="section-label">WhatsApp for CPA Firms</span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mt-4">
            How it works in practice
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue/10 border border-blue/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-blue font-bold text-lg">1</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">Set up your client list and required documents</h3>
              <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
                Upload your client list, mark what you need from each one — pay stubs, invoices, tax certificates, whatever's needed.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue/10 border border-blue/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-blue font-bold text-lg">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">HeshbonAI sends automatic reminders from your business number</h3>
              <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
                Messages go out from your firm's number, with your name and logo. Clients receive a personalized message in the right tone.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue/10 border border-blue/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-blue font-bold text-lg">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">The client snaps a photo and sends it right in WhatsApp</h3>
              <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
                The client just photographs the document and sends it. Exactly like sending a photo to a friend. Zero friction, zero hassle.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue/10 border border-blue/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-blue font-bold text-lg">4</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">The system confirms, classifies, and updates your team</h3>
              <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
                HeshbonAI identifies the document type, confirms receipt to the client, and updates your team in real time. No manual tracking.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WhatsApp Chat Mockup -->
    <section class="bg-navy-light py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-10">
          <span class="section-label">Automated Client Reminders</span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-4">
            What it looks like from the client's side
          </h2>
        </div>
        <!-- WhatsApp Chat Mockup -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border shadow-2xl max-w-md mx-auto">
          <!-- WhatsApp Header -->
          <div class="bg-[#1F2C34] px-4 py-3 flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-7 3c1.93 0 3.5 1.57 3.5 3.5S13.93 13 12 13s-3.5-1.57-3.5-3.5S10.07 6 12 6zm7 13H5v-.23c0-.62.28-1.2.76-1.58C7.47 15.82 9.64 15 12 15s4.53.82 6.24 2.19c.48.38.76.97.76 1.58V19z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-white text-sm font-semibold">Williams &amp; Partners CPA</div>
              <div class="text-[#8696A0] text-xs">Verified business account</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Chat Body -->
          <div class="bg-[#0B141A] px-3 py-4 space-y-3 min-h-[320px]">
            <!-- Outgoing (from business) -->
            <div class="flex justify-end">
              <div class="bg-[#005C4B] rounded-lg rounded-tr-none px-3 py-2 max-w-[85%] shadow">
                <p class="text-[#E9EDEF] text-sm leading-relaxed">
                  Hi Sarah, we need 3 documents for your annual return. You can send them right here:
                </p>
                <p class="text-[#E9EDEF] text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">
                  1. W-2 from employer<br/>
                  2. 1099 forms (if any)<br/>
                  3. Year-end bank statement
                </p>
                <div class="text-[#8696A0] text-[10px] text-right mt-1 flex items-center gap-1 justify-end">
                  09:14
                  <svg class="w-4 h-3 text-[#53BDEB]" viewBox="0 0 16 11" fill="currentColor"><path d="M11.07.66L4.88 6.85 2.6 4.57l-.7.7 2.98 2.98.7-.7 6.19-6.19-.7-.7zM6.58 9.55l-.7-.7-2.28-2.28-.7.7 2.98 2.98.7-.7zM12.47 1.36l-.7-.7-4.79 4.79.7.7 4.79-4.79z"/></svg>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Incoming (from client) -->
            <div class="flex justify-start">
              <div class="bg-[#1F2C34] rounded-lg rounded-tl-none px-3 py-2 max-w-[85%] shadow">
                <p class="text-[#E9EDEF] text-sm leading-relaxed">
                  Sure thing, let me grab those
                </p>
                <div class="text-[#8696A0] text-[10px] text-right mt-1">09:15</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Incoming (from client - document) -->
            <div class="flex justify-start">
              <div class="bg-[#1F2C34] rounded-lg rounded-tl-none px-3 py-2 max-w-[85%] shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#0B141A] rounded-lg p-2 mb-1">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#8696A0]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m2.25 0H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z" /></svg>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-[#E9EDEF] text-xs font-medium">W2_2025_Sarah_Mitchell.pdf</div>
                    <div class="text-[#8696A0] text-[10px]">PDF - 245 KB</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[#E9EDEF] text-sm">Here's the first one</p>
                <div class="text-[#8696A0] text-[10px] text-right mt-1">09:17</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Outgoing (confirmation) -->
            <div class="flex justify-end">
              <div class="bg-[#005C4B] rounded-lg rounded-tr-none px-3 py-2 max-w-[85%] shadow">
                <p class="text-[#E9EDEF] text-sm leading-relaxed">
                  Got your W-2, thanks Sarah! 2 documents remaining. Take your time.
                </p>
                <div class="text-[#8696A0] text-[10px] text-right mt-1 flex items-center gap-1 justify-end">
                  09:17
                  <svg class="w-4 h-3 text-[#53BDEB]" viewBox="0 0 16 11" fill="currentColor"><path d="M11.07.66L4.88 6.85 2.6 4.57l-.7.7 2.98 2.98.7-.7 6.19-6.19-.7-.7zM6.58 9.55l-.7-.7-2.28-2.28-.7.7 2.98 2.98.7-.7zM12.47 1.36l-.7-.7-4.79 4.79.7.7 4.79-4.79z"/></svg>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm text-center mt-6">
          * Example for illustration only. Messages are sent from your firm's branded business number.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section class="bg-navy py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <span class="section-label">Features</span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mt-4">
            Why WhatsApp and not another portal
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="mb-4">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">No downloads needed — the client is already there</h3>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              No need to convince anyone to download an app or create an account. WhatsApp is already on every client's phone. Just send a message and start working.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="mb-4">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Smart scheduling — respects weekends and holidays</h3>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              The system knows when not to send: weekends, public holidays, unreasonable hours. Automated reminders only go out at the right times, at a frequency that won't annoy.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="mb-4">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 8.511c.884.284 1.5 1.128 1.5 2.097v4.286c0 1.136-.847 2.1-1.98 2.193-.34.027-.68.052-1.02.072v3.091l-3-3c-1.354 0-2.694-.055-4.02-.163a2.115 2.115 0 01-.825-.242m9.345-8.334a2.126 2.126 0 00-.476-.095 48.64 48.64 0 00-8.048 0c-1.131.094-1.976 1.057-1.976 2.192v4.286c0 .837.46 1.58 1.155 1.951m9.345-8.334V6.637c0-1.621-1.152-3.026-2.76-3.235A48.455 48.455 0 0011.25 3c-2.115 0-4.198.137-6.24.402-1.608.209-2.76 1.614-2.76 3.235v6.226c0 1.621 1.152 3.026 2.76 3.235.577.075 1.157.14 1.74.194V21l4.155-4.155" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">CPAs can message the assistant too</h3>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              Need to request a document from a specific client? Send a message to HeshbonAI directly from your own WhatsApp and the system handles it. No need to open any dashboard.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="mb-4">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Branded business number — your firm's name and logo</h3>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              Messages are sent from a verified WhatsApp Business account with your firm's name, logo, and description. The client sees it's really you, not spam.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section class="bg-navy-light border-t border-border py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">
          Ready to let WhatsApp work for you?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted mt-4 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Let HeshbonAI handle the reminders and document collection. You focus on what you do best — delivering professional service to your clients.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mt-10">
          <a href="https://cal.com/heshbonai/intro" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">
            Schedule your intro call
          </a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4">
            See Pricing
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
